nce 2-5 as final scoreline and won against both Honduras and Ecuador to qualify for the round of 16 having 6 points on the table next to group leader France. After that, in the round of 16, they drew with the Finalist Argentina and loss 0-1 to get knocked out of the tournament.</p>
